I've put

51
00:06:30,780 --> 00:06:31,900
your microscope here.

52
00:06:35,380 --> 00:06:36,180
Mr. Gu,

53
00:06:36,260 --> 00:06:37,820
you really put in the effort.

54
00:06:38,180 --> 00:06:39,100
It was just a quick tidy-up.

55
00:06:39,860 --> 00:06:40,740
Thank you so much.

56
00:06:40,780 --> 00:06:41,580
Look,

57
00:06:42,380 --> 00:06:43,900
although he's also wearing a white coat,

58
00:06:44,060 --> 00:06:46,580
he doesn't look like a food server.

59
00:06:46,860 --> 00:06:47,860
And who does?

60
